title: Introduction to Free Trade Agreements | Exporting Basics Episode 17
description:
This video offers guidance on the advantages and opportunities that US free trade agreements provide. FTAs can make it easier to ship your product overseas. Watch the exporting video brought to you by Export.Gov to learn about US exporting agreements that you could qualify for. For more: https://www.export.gov/article?id=U-S-Free-Trade-Agreements--Introduction
